    <description>Miracle.Settings replaces error prone local loading of AppSettings with strong typed objects.
Load multiple settings into a strong typed object with two lines of codes:

ISettingsLoader settingsLoader = new SettingsLoader();
var settings = settingsLoader.Create&gt;MyCustomSettingsClass&lt;();

Supports nested objects, arrays, lists and dictionaries.
Custom converter system supporting Enum, Guid, Timespan and Uri. Add your own converters with one line of code. 
